item.title: Demonoid is back up
item.dc:creator: @Ron Ron
item.description:
@Ron wrote:

I love demonoid and am so glad it’s back up. Surprised to see that 3 out of 8 of my torrents survived. Oh well, they had their time in the spotlight.

Glad someone made a thread to let the public know. 3 years ago we were trying to spread demonoid to different forums and since I was a part of this one, we started making keys and spreading it here. Now so many people are informed about how awesome of a tracker it is, several years later it comes back up and there is immediately a post on this forum to note that fact.

I <3 humanity (and torrents)

~Ron
